profile: Guelph & Orangeville Building and Landscape Supply provides superior construction products from lumber to landscaping.  We supply building and landscape materials to the Guelph and Orangeville area, Dufferin/Wellington County and surrounding markets. We offer the highest quality natural stone, mulch, decorative stone, pavers and other landscaping tools and supplies. We also carry many other construction materials including drywall, masonry tools and insulation. Customer service remains our number one value, and is matched up by superior products, reputable suppliers, and an incredible staff.
